      "leftCol": "\n      <div class=\"sec-head\"><div class=\"sec-lbl\">KEY POINTS</div><div class=\"sec-line\"></div></div>\n\n      <div class=\"pc\">\n        <div class=\"pc-accent\"></div>\n        <div class=\"pc-icon\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\"><polyline points=\"2,14 7,8 11,11 18,4\" stroke=\"#3D3D3D\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></polyline><polyline points=\"14,4 18,4 18,8\" stroke=\"#3D3D3D\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></polyline></svg></div>\n        <div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-main\">YouTube台本市場は今も需要がある</div><div class=\"pc-note\">スカッと系・ゆっくり解説・ノウハウ系の3ジャンルが初心者の入り口</div></div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"pc\">\n        <div class=\"pc-accent\"></div>\n        <div class=\"pc-icon\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"10\" cy=\"10\" r=\"8\" stroke=\"#3D3D3D\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></circle><path d=\"M10 6V10L13 13\" stroke=\"#3D3D3D\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></div>\n        <div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-main\">最初から速く書けなくて普通</div><div class=\"pc-note\">1本6〜8時間は当然。Gemini活用＋型で2〜3時間へ短縮できる</div></div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"pc\">\n        <div class=\"pc-accent\"></div>\n        <div class=\"pc-icon\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"10\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\" stroke=\"#3D3D3D\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></circle><path d=\"M2 18c0-4 3.58-7 8-7s8 3 8 7\" stroke=\"#3D3D3D\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></div>\n        <div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-main\">最初は低単価でも実績作りを優先する</div><div class=\"pc-note\">0.3〜0.5円からスタート。評価と実績を積んでから単価を上げる</div></div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"pc hl\">\n        <div class=\"pc-accent\"></div>\n        <div class=\"pc-icon\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M10 2